# Willbe Trends Standards

- Keep research logic in `src/willbe_trends/research/`; LLM wiring in `src/willbe_trends/llm/`.
- All new providers implement `LLMProvider` and register in `llm/registry.py`.
- Model outputs must parse into Pydantic models — never return raw LLM text to callers.
- Prompt changes belong next to the research module they serve; update `specs/` when behavior changes.
- Prefer async LLM calls; CLI wraps with `asyncio.run`.
- Use Typer for CLI commands; Rich for terminal output.
- Sample inputs live in `samples/`; product behavior docs live in `specs/`.
